"Remove all files and folders in the <filename>tmp/</filename> subdirectory. "
"The <filename>tmp/</filename> subdirectory is created after running a "
"<command>make</command> command to build a book, such as <command>make html</"
"command>."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: command
